2. Mnemonic Trick (C-S-N-D-I-M-M)
Remember categories in this order:

ğŸ”¹ Compute
ğŸ”¹ Storage
ğŸ”¹ Network
ğŸ”¹ Database
ğŸ”¹ Identity
ğŸ”¹ Monitoring
ğŸ”¹ Management

